StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_GetPhaselineObjec.ves]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@Organiza.onID as integer, @FiscalYear as integer, @Month as integer AS
SELECT PHASELINE_ID, ISNULL(ATTAIN_PERCENT, 0) AS ATTAIN_PERCENT, CONVERT(varchar(20), START_DATE, 106) AS START_DATE, CONVERT(varchar(20), END_DATE, 106) AS END_DATE FROM PHASELINE_OBJECTIVE WHERE ORGANIZATION_ID = @Organiza.onID AND FISCAL_YEAR = @FiscalYear AND MONTH = @Month ORDER BY START_DATE
